<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="however-conj">however <strong><em>conj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /haʊ'evə(r)/    美 /haʊ'evər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-no-matter-how">1.★ <strong>[相当于no matter how, 引导让步状语从句] 不管用什么方法 / 方式：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>However I approached the problem, I couldn't find a solution.
不管用什么办法，我都无法解决这个问题。</p></div></div>